<text><body>
<lb n="0869b08"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0869b09"/>
<lb n="0869b10"/><head type="no">No. 145 [Nos. 125(52.1), 144]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0869b11"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>佛母般泥洹經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0869b12"/>
<lb n="0869b13"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0869011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（劉）＋宋【元】【明】</note><app n="0869011"><lem>宋</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">劉宋</rdg></app>沙門<note n="0869012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（釋）＋慧【三】</note><note n="0869012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（釋）＋慧【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869012"><lem>慧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">釋慧</rdg></app>簡譯</byline>
<lb n="0869b14"/><p>聞如是。一時佛在維耶<note n="0869013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">離＝梨【三】＊</note><note n="0869013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">離＝梨【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869013"><lem>離</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">梨</rdg></app>國。行在獼猴水邊
<lb n="0869b15"/>拘羅曷講堂上。大愛道比丘尼者即<note n="0869014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從佛＝佛姨【三】</note><note n="0869014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從佛＝佛姨【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869014"><lem>從佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">佛姨</rdg></app>母
<lb n="0869b16"/>也。時在維耶<anchor id="fxT02p0869b01"/>離國。與<note n="0869015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">女除饉＝除饉女【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0869015"><lem>女除饉</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">除饉女</rdg></app>五百人俱。皆
<lb n="0869b17"/>是應真。獲六通四達神足變化。年<note n="0869016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耆＝長【三】</note><note n="0869016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耆＝長【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869016"><lem>耆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">長</rdg></app>德尊神
<lb n="0869b18"/><note n="0869017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曜＝燿【三】＊</note><note n="0869017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曜＝燿【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869017"><lem>曜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">燿</rdg></app>巍巍。其精舍在王園所度無量深入普智
<lb n="0869b19"/>定。&CB00418;世尊逮阿難<note n="0869018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鶖鷺＝秋露【宋】＊</note><app n="0869018"><lem>鶖鷺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">秋露</rdg></app>子大目<note n="0869019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乾〕－【三】</note><note n="0869019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔乾〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869019"><lem>乾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>連。所度
<lb n="0869b20"/>已畢將欲滅度日。吾不忍見世尊如來無所
<lb n="0869b21"/>著正真道最正覺及諸應真<note n="0869020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔泥曰〕－【三】</note><note n="0869020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔泥曰〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869020"><lem>泥曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。吾當先息
<lb n="0869b22"/>靈還<note n="0869021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乎＝于【三】</note><note n="0869021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乎＝于【宋】【元】【明】<corr resp="say" sic="">＊</corr></note><app n="0869021"><lem>乎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">于</rdg></app>本無矣。佛一切智具照其然。即告阿
<lb n="0869b23"/>難。大愛道念曰。吾不忍見世尊并諸應真泥
<lb n="0869b24"/><note n="0869022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰＝洹【三】＊</note><note n="0869022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰＝洹【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869022"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">洹</rdg></app>。欲先滅度阿難聞教即稽首言。今聞尊
<lb n="0869b25"/>命。四體萎墮心塞智索。不識四方之名。佛告
<lb n="0869b26"/>阿難。汝謂大愛道滅度將戒種慧種<note n="0869023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔定種〕－【三】</note><note n="0869023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔定種〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869023"><lem>定種</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>解
<lb n="0869b27"/>脫種度知見種。<note n="0869024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕－【三】</note><note n="0869024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔若〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869024"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>四意止四意斷四神足五
<lb n="0869b28"/>根五力七覺意八<note n="0869025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔品〕－【三】</note><note n="0869025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔品〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869025"><lem>品</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>道行去耶。對曰。不也。
<lb n="0869b29"/>但惟佛生七日<note n="0869026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝太【三】</note><note n="0869026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大＝太【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869026"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">太</rdg></app>后薨。母慈至有<note n="0869027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【三】</note><note n="0869027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869027"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>弘恩。
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0145.0869c" n="0869c"/>
<lb n="0869c01"/>在佛所耳。世尊歎曰。真如汝言。母於吾誠有
<lb n="0869c02"/>哺乳重恩之惠。吾亦有難算之恩在母所也。
<lb n="0869c03"/><note n="0869028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">由＝猶【宋】</note><app n="0869028"><lem>由</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">猶</rdg></app>吾明獲歸命佛歸命法歸命聖眾。自歸
<lb n="0869c04"/><note n="0869029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">習＝集【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0869029"><lem>習</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">集</rdg></app><note n="0869030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡道＝道盡【三】＊</note><note n="0869030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡道＝道盡【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869030"><lem>盡道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">道盡</rdg></app>冥滅明盛。無疑於三尊苦<anchor id="fxT02p0869c01"/>習盡道
<lb n="0869c05"/>道眼明盡解結解獲無所著。若人能<note n="0869031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悟＝寤【宋】</note><app n="0869031"><lem>悟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">寤</rdg></app>愚者
<lb n="0869c06"/>之惑。令入<note n="0869032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正真＝真正【三】＊</note><note n="0869032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">正真＝真正【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869032"><lem>正真</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">真正</rdg></app>歸佛歸法歸<anchor id="fxT02p0869c02"/>乎聖眾。自歸
<lb n="0869c07"/><anchor id="fxT02p0869c03"/>習<anchor id="fxT02p0869c04"/>盡道者。受道弟子。盡天下名珍。訖其年
<lb n="0869c08"/>壽供養經師。萬未<note n="0869033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">塞＝賽【元】【明】</note><app n="0869033"><lem>塞</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">賽</rdg></app>一。歸命三尊恩過須
<lb n="0869c09"/>彌。弟子<note n="0869034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">由＝猶【元】【明】</note><app n="0869034"><lem>由</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">猶</rdg></app>芥子也。是故阿難。吾有重恩於
<lb n="0869c10"/>大愛道<note n="0869035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔所〕－【宋】</note><app n="0869035"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。其為無量<note n="0869036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＝矣【三】</note><note n="0869036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也＝矣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869036"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">矣</rdg></app><note n="0869037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於時〕－【宋】</note><app n="0869037"><lem>於時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>大愛道與除
<lb n="0869c11"/>饉女五百人俱到佛所。<note n="0869038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔皆〕－【三】</note><note n="0869038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔皆〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869038"><lem>皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>頭面著<note n="0869039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【三】</note><note n="0869039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869039"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>足退
<lb n="0869c12"/>叉手立。大愛道白佛言。吾不忍&CB00418;佛及諸應
<lb n="0869c13"/>真滅度。欲先泥<anchor id="fxT02p0869c05"/>曰。佛默可之。大愛道以手
<lb n="0869c14"/>摩佛足曰。吾免&CB00418;如來應儀正真道最正覺
<lb n="0869c15"/>道法御天人師三界明。自今不復&CB00418;之矣。五
<lb n="0869c16"/>百除饉女陳辭如上。佛亦可之也。為說身患
<lb n="0869c17"/>生死憂悲苦不如意<note n="0869040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00478;＝惱【三】＊</note><note n="0869040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00478;＝惱【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869040"><lem>&CB00478;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">惱</rdg></app><note n="0869041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之難〕－【宋】</note><app n="0869041"><lem>之難</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="0869042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（又嘆）＋無【三】</note><note n="0869042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（又嘆）＋無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869042"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">又嘆無</rdg></app>欲清淨空
<lb n="0869c18"/>不願無<note n="0869043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">相＝想【三】＊</note><note n="0869043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相＝想【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869043"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">想</rdg></app>滅度之安若干淨品。諸女除饉莫
<lb n="0869c19"/>不歡喜。繞佛三匝稽首而去。還<note n="0869044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乎＝于【宋】【元】，於【明】</note><note n="0869044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乎＝于【宋】【元】，＝於【明】</note><app n="0869044"><lem>乎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">于</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">於</rdg></app>精舍布五
<lb n="0869c20"/>百座皆各就<note n="0869045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝座【三】＊</note><note n="0869045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐＝座【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869045"><lem>坐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">座</rdg></app>。大愛道現神足德。自<anchor id="fxT02p0869c06"/>坐沒
<lb n="0869c21"/>地從東方來。在虛空中化。去地一樹轉昇<note n="0869046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（至）＋七【三】</note><note n="0869046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（至）＋七【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869046"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">至七</rdg></app>
<lb n="0869c22"/>樹。經行虛空中。乍坐乍臥。上身出水。下身出
<lb n="0869c23"/>火。下身出水。上身出火。又沒地中<note n="0869047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飛東＝飛從西【三】＊</note><note n="0869047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飛東＝飛從西【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869047"><lem>飛東</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">飛從西</rdg></app>方
<lb n="0869c24"/>來。沒法如前。八方上下來。放大光明以照諸
<lb n="0869c25"/>冥中。人上<anchor id="fxT02p0869c07"/>曜諸天。五百除饉變化俱然同時
<lb n="0869c26"/>泥<anchor id="fxT02p0869c08"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0869c27"/><p>佛告賢者阿難。汝明旦入城到耶游理家所
<lb n="0869c28"/>告之曰。佛母及五百耆年除饉皆<note n="0869048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝如【明】</note><app n="0869048"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>滅度。
<lb n="0869c29"/>佛勸理家作五百輿床。麻油香花樟柟梓<note n="0869049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">事＝木【三】</note><note n="0869049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">事＝木【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869049"><lem>事</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">木</rdg></app>
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0145.0870a" n="0870a"/>
<lb n="0870a01"/>各五百。貢妓正音當以供養所以然者。斯諸
<lb n="0870a02"/>除饉皆六通四達。獲空不願無<anchor id="fxT02p0870a01"/>相淨定。今得
<lb n="0870a03"/>泥<anchor id="fxT02p0870a02"/>曰為諸佛所歎。一時之供養其福無數。阿
<lb n="0870a04"/>難稽首于地惻然敬諾。平旦入城至理家門。
<lb n="0870a05"/>告守門者曰。入云吾來。門人入如事云。理家
<lb n="0870a06"/>時在高觀與樂人相娛。聞阿難來心怖毛<note n="0870001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00594;＝豎【明】</note><app n="0870001"><lem>&CB00594;</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">豎</rdg></app>
<lb n="0870a07"/>即下觀疾出五體投地。以<note n="0870002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">手＝首【三】</note><note n="0870002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">手＝首【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870002"><lem>手</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">首</rdg></app>著足長跪而曰。
<lb n="0870a08"/>賢者</p>
<lb n="0870a09"/><p>阿難今來甚早。斯事非&M010527;將以何故。阿難如
<lb n="0870a10"/>佛教具為理家說之。理家聞之即<note n="0870003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">擗＝&CB00570;【三】</note><note n="0870003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">擗＝&CB00570;【宋】【元】【明】<corr resp="say" sic="">＊</corr></note><app n="0870003"><lem>擗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00570;</rdg></app>身于地。
<lb n="0870a11"/>抗哀而云。吾等豈有非佛弟子。不肖之行而
<lb n="0870a12"/>為除饉所棄矣。長逝無為而無遺教乎。噓唏
<lb n="0870a13"/>重曰。賢者阿難<note n="0870004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＋（今）【三】</note><note n="0870004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自＋（今）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870004"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">自今</rdg></app>維耶梨精舍都為空寂。王
<lb n="0870a14"/>道四街不復&CB00418;神通女除饉。如彼<note n="0870005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盛＝威【元】【明】</note><app n="0870005"><lem>盛</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">威</rdg></app>德行于
<lb n="0870a15"/>國道。國道為空其痛何甚乎。阿難答曰。佛說
<lb n="0870a16"/>乾坤雖為長久始必有終。盛者有衰恩愛當
<lb n="0870a17"/>離。&CB00418;異欲<note n="0870006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">永＝乖【三】</note><note n="0870006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">永＝乖【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870006"><lem>永</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">乖</rdg></app>者尋行受報。三界無常其如幻
<lb n="0870a18"/>夢。古來非常苦身之患其禍無量。而愚者不
<lb n="0870a19"/>見可謂瞽矣。生求不死。會<note n="0870007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畢＝冀【三】</note><note n="0870007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畢＝冀【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870007"><lem>畢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">冀</rdg></app>不離者終不可
<lb n="0870a20"/>得也。上賢&CB00418;佛經奧解四非常如盲得視。精
<lb n="0870a21"/>進勤行可免重苦矣。阿難引若干要說。以釋
<lb n="0870a22"/>理家結。理家心解即喜。阿難復至諸梵志理
<lb n="0870a23"/>家所。時其眾在講堂有異議。即告之曰。佛勸
<lb n="0870a24"/>諸賢者作五百人葬具。所以然者。佛母并五
<lb n="0870a25"/>百<anchor id="fxT02p0870a03"/>女除饉皆已滅度。梵志理家聞阿難言靡
<lb n="0870a26"/>不<anchor id="fxT02p0870a04"/>擗地椎心<note n="0870008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搣＝滅【三】</note><note n="0870008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">搣＝滅【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870008"><lem>搣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">滅</rdg></app>髮宛轉哀號云。當奈何。吾
<lb n="0870a27"/>等孤露將腹誰恃乎。阿難又說。三界是幻都
<lb n="0870a28"/>為非常身為苦器<anchor id="fxT02p0870a05"/>&CB00478;痛所聚唯泥<anchor id="fxT02p0870a06"/>曰安故三
<lb n="0870a29"/>尊歸之也。理家心解稽首足下。阿難還至佛
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0145.0870b" n="0870b"/>
<lb n="0870b01"/>所。如事以聞。梵志理家即具葬具。馳詣精舍
<lb n="0870b02"/>時園門閉。理家使人緣入開門欲入講堂。有
<lb n="0870b03"/>女沙彌<note n="0870009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝六【宋】</note><app n="0870009"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">六</rdg></app>人。一人得不還道。次者頻來。小
<lb n="0870b04"/>者溝港。告理家曰。吾師坐禪今得寂定。慎無
<lb n="0870b05"/>擾也。答曰。師已滅度不為定也。沙彌聞之。
<lb n="0870b06"/><anchor id="fxT02p0870b01"/>擗身絕息有頃乃<note n="0870010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穌＝蘇【三】</note><note n="0870010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">穌＝蘇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870010"><lem>穌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">蘇</rdg></app>。哀號而曰。誰當復誨
<lb n="0870b07"/>吾等聖訓<note n="0870011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">絕＋（矣）【三】</note><note n="0870011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">絕＋（矣）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870011"><lem>絕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">絕矣</rdg></app>吾者廢也。理家&CB00418;之莫不舉哀。
<lb n="0870b08"/>哀畢告沙彌曰。佛本說經。恩愛雖會終必有
<lb n="0870b09"/>離。世榮難保唯道可久。但當建志進取應真。
<lb n="0870b10"/>滅三界苦捐俗哀心也。理家闍維畢。奉舍利
<lb n="0870b11"/>詣佛所。佛告<anchor id="fxT02p0870b02"/>鶖鷺子。汝東向叉手下右膝
<lb n="0870b12"/>曰。有直信直業三神六智道神已足者。皆來
<lb n="0870b13"/>赴斯。所以然者。佛母逮諸<anchor id="fxT02p0870b03"/>除饉女五百人今
<lb n="0870b14"/>皆善逝。宜當<note n="0870012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（法）＋會【三】</note><note n="0870012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（法）＋會【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870012"><lem>會</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">法會</rdg></app>四方俱然。於是四方各二百
<lb n="0870b15"/>五十應真。神足飛來稽首佛足。佛起至大愛
<lb n="0870b16"/>道舍利所。千比丘從皆就<note n="0870013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（座佛）＋告【三】</note><note n="0870013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（座佛）＋告【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870013"><lem>告</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">座佛告</rdg></app>阿難。取舍利盛
<lb n="0870b17"/>之以&CB00425;著吾手中。阿難如命。以&CB00425;盛舍利長
<lb n="0870b18"/>跪授佛。佛以兩手受之。告諸比丘。斯聚舍利。
<lb n="0870b19"/>本是穢身凶愚急暴。輕心疾轉嫉<note n="0870014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姤＝&CB00107;【三】</note><note n="0870014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姤＝&CB00107;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870014"><lem>姤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00107;</rdg></app>陰謀。敗
<lb n="0870b20"/>道壞德為亂作先之類。今母拔女人兇愚之
<lb n="0870b21"/>穢。為丈夫行獲應真道。<note n="0870015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔還〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0870015"><lem>還</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>靈本無淨過虛
<lb n="0870b22"/>空。行高<note n="0870016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＋（盡）【宋】【元】</note><app n="0870016"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">無盡</rdg></app>蓋何其健哉。佛告諸比丘及理家
<lb n="0870b23"/>眾。共為母及諸應真女興廟。僉曰唯然。於是
<lb n="0870b24"/>天人鬼龍興廟立<note n="0870017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">剎＝表【三】</note><note n="0870017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">剎＝表【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870017"><lem>剎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">表</rdg></app>。華香作樂繞廟三匝。哀
<lb n="0870b25"/><note n="0870018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝音【三】</note><note n="0870018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者＝音【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870018"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">音</rdg></app>震國詣佛敬信。輒說生死為苦三界無安
<lb n="0870b26"/>以釋來者。莫不歡喜。稽首而去</p>
<lb n="0870b27"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛母般泥洹<note n="0870019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宋】【元】</note><app n="0870019"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">經一卷</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
<lb n="0870b28"/><div1 type="W"><head><note n="0870020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此記無於麗依宋元明載</note>佛般泥洹後變記</head>
<lb n="0870b29"/><p>我般泥洹後百歲我諸弟子沙門。聰明智
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0145.0870c" n="0870c"/>
<lb n="0870c01"/>慧如我無異。我般泥洹後二百歲時。阿育
<lb n="0870c02"/>王從八王索八斛四斗舍利。一日中作八
<lb n="0870c03"/>萬四千佛圖。三百歲時。若有出家作沙門。
<lb n="0870c04"/>一日中便得道。四百歲時。數念佛及法以
<lb n="0870c05"/>比丘僧。供養和<note n="0870021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＝尚【明】</note><app n="0870021"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">尚</rdg></app>阿闍梨。五百歲時。沙
<lb n="0870c06"/>門婆羅門及人民。無不啼泣念佛者。六百
<lb n="0870c07"/>歲時。諸沙門便行入山中樹下塚間求道。
<lb n="0870c08"/>七百歲時。便行內外學經。若有沙門婆羅
<lb n="0870c09"/>門問事無不解了。悉壞九十六種外道。八
<lb n="0870c10"/>百歲時。便復念行作佛圖<note n="0870022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02680;＝&CB01819;【元】【明】</note><app n="0870022"><lem>&CB02680;</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB01819;</rdg></app>疾次作佛圖。
<lb n="0870c11"/>九百歲時。便念行治生求利害處所。千歲
<lb n="0870c12"/>時。便行與國王相隨教習兵法戰陣。自行
<lb n="0870c13"/>屠殺妻娶婦女</p>
<lb n="0870c14"/><p>佛般泥洹後變記</p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
